{"tid":2153317,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［！！］NYT獨家《奢華豪宅、中共權貴的財富與香港的命運》講粟戰書個女 栗潛心","createTime":"2020-08-12T12:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T13:56:38.000Z","uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4e706b4bc0d62667eeae4dbbe7b77c5ae5412194","tid":2153317,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T12:38:19.000Z","msg":"香港&mdash;&mdash;作為中國共產黨第三號領導人物的長女，栗潛心在香港悄悄打造出一種橫跨這座城市金融精英和中國政治隱秘世界的生活。<br />\n<br />\n多年來，透過以給官員子女鋪路著稱的香港和大陸職場人士俱樂部，她與國企高管們談笑風生。她是中國的省級政治顧問團體的香港代表。她還是一家總部位於香港的國有投資銀行的主席，該銀行長期以來一直與中國高層官員的親屬做生意。<br />\n<br />\n栗潛心現年38歲，在這座城市也有著深厚的財力基礎，購買了一幢價值1500萬美元的四層海景聯排別墅。她的伴侶擁有一匹現已退役的賽馬，並斥資數億入股赫赫有名的半島酒店，後來已將股份出售⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/business/20200812/china-hong-kong-elite/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fbusiness%2F20200812%2Fchina-hong-kong-elite%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7SMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=b2e989bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/business/20200812/china-hong-kong-elite/zh-hant/</a>"},{"pid":"2f760bea91fdd734a1372ab732af62e2917d04c5","tid":2153317,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T12:39:42.000Z","msg":"作者twitter有英文版link、跟進討論<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/pekingmike/status/1293500266164125697?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpekingmike%2Fstatus%2F1293500266164125697%3Fs%3D21&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7SMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=69476541\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpekingmike%2Fstatus%2F1293500266164125697%3Fs%3D21&h=3efde748\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/pekingmike/status/1293500266164125697?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"ca6838f4c30b910b262193ef3ee48e24c0deef08","tid":2153317,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T12:40:50.000Z","msg":"果然潛心搵銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c96285f86131a01f465cfefd971937cf79c9a6","tid":2153317,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T12:40:56.000Z","msg":"【中環人語】有權勢就有財勢 習總大內總管潛港起底｜壹週刊<br />\n大酒店被坡仔蔡華波接貨，仲扯出大內總管栗戰書嗰女栗潛心，同佢大有關係。兩人同樣報住赤柱灘道六號，物業前身名為麗安閣，是新華社接待政要及上賓之地，前社長周南亦曾居於此。○七年由中國海外向中聯辦收購重建為豪宅，四年前由栗潛心為董事的海外公司，以$1.17億購入其中一間獨立屋，栗潛心曾任建銀資產管理聯席董事，現時在中信資本做副總裁，亦是紅色商會華菁會的名譽董事；蔡華波出手掃10%大酒店，資金動輒要廿億，自然財來自有方。 <br />\n<br />\n以大陸官場之哲學，有權勢就有財富，栗潛心父親栗戰書是習近平愛將，任中共中央辦公廳主任，祖父栗政修為中共地下黨員。蔡華波同此深紅女子行得咁埋，掃起你大酒店都咪話冇可能！ <br />\n<br />\n撰文：宗菁華 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_529498_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_529498_0&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7SMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=ceb7ed59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_529498_0&h=3ba17033\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_529498_0</a>"},{"pid":"b64ae4898960df652a3c45bb43c3a65c8c409b99","tid":2153317,"uid":202577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T12:43:05.000Z","msg":"正野"},{"pid":"93ae4e10ccf18916c517f227561ace674febcf1c","tid":2153317,"uid":292208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T12:44:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9422c6b983e7badb626f602a3fec55901816f0aa","tid":2153317,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T12:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d41adadc791163e8296445813f365d8f4bdf739","tid":2153317,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T12:46:50.000Z","msg":"聯署支持封殺微信同TikTok<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpeti